      "content": "right, i get the systemic stuff, but for my bibliography i need to see the actual trends. can u give me some more specifics on which groups are most frequently cited in these stats? like, can u break down the correlation for black and hispanic populations vs white populations? i just need the raw statistical overview of how the crime rates compare across those specific groups.",
